devdoc.details: This contract allows only the owner to modify a count variable within a defined range.

add(int256).details: Adds a value to the count, ensuring it stays within the allowed range.

constructor.details: Sets the contract deployer as the owner.

getCount().details: Returns the current count value. Only the owner can view it.

returns._0: The current count as an integer.

subtract(int256).details: Subtracts a value from the count, ensuring it stays within the allowed range.

devdoc.title: RestrictedCount Contract
